About Us
Mount Dora Golf Club is billed as “the longest 5,700 yards in Florida,” which is high praise for this par 70, 88 acre challenge with both down and uphill lies, to keep the best golfers on their toes. Meanwhile, this course taps into the beauty of the Florida landscape to help rookies relax as they ease into this classic game. Mount Dora Golf Club truly gives its players the
best of both worlds.
Our course is open to the public seven days a week from 7 a.m. until dark, and we also have a putting green and practice area for you to hone your game!
